{"tid":1605402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唇茶：如果著黑衫行街/返屋企食飯比狗截，記得話係出黎買嘢飲！因為買一送一真係好抵！","createTime":"2019-09-30T09:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T09:30:01.000Z","uid":120970,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"646132032de68b680ce7d5b7c2aa81b5d0287e35","tid":1605402,"uid":120970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:30:01.000Z","msg":"早幾日佢地鋪頭ig有po講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fmJxBZv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfmJxBZv.png&h=9c5aaa3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日飲食男女有埋報導<br />\n良心小店講到明 個活動係突登撐我地！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">老闆Asum表示，「選在國慶日，並沒有特別意思，只是當日有個『全民黑衣日』活動，所以就推出這優惠。我相信當日應該會很多人站出來，如果覺得天氣熱，要避暑，都可以隨時入來。」<br />\n<br />\n他有感最近社會氣氛緊繃，「好像隨便穿件黑衣，出去就會被警察拘捕」，自己及員工亦曾因制服是黑色，被警察查問，所以希望活動可以對市民送上支持。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【逆權小店】10.1全民黑衣日 茶飲店推優惠 著黑衫減$5或買一送一 老闆：黑衫不是恐怖份子<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=3_60083697&amp;i=20190930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D3_60083697%26i%3D20190930&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=7da7ebbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D3_60083697%26i%3D20190930&h=3aec105c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=3_60083697&amp;i=20190930</a>"}]}